Thank you for your interest in our friendly community Professionally Managed by Cannon Management! We are excited to work with you! Please note that our availability changes daily and our prices may vary.<br>
<br>
Summer Meadows are just two blocks from UC Riverside Campus, close to the freeway and minutes to University Village. Enjoy easy walking and biking through Box Springs Mountain Reserve and the University Village retail promenade, which offers the best dining, shopping and entertainment.<br>
<br>
Our spacious one, two and three bedroom floor plans at Summer Meadows feature gourmet kitchens and enclosed backyards or patios. As a resident, you'll enjoy all the amenities created to make your life a dream come true. Take a refreshing dip in our refreshing swimming pool and spa area with Wi-Fi. If youâ€™re up for the challenge, organize some teams for an exciting game of cornhole or ping-pong. Sit down and relax at our picnic area with beautiful stainless steel barbecues to cook up some delicious meals for your friends or family. We are a pet-friendly community and green-friendly as well. See why Summer Meadows Apartments the ideal place to rent in Riverside, CA!<br>
<br>
Application process is quick and easy!<br>
First time renters are always welcomed.<br>
Just bring in a $100 Money Order to the office and reserve your spot now!<br>
All units are at a first come first serve basis so don't miss out!<br>
Application fee is $40/Applicant 18+<br>
Call to check availability!!<br>
<br>
These BEAUTIFUL apartments include:<br>
Gas stove<br>
Fridge**<br>
Dishwasher<br>
Central AC and Heating<br>
Spacious Bedrooms<br>
<br>
PET FRIENDLY!<br>
*Pet deposit of $300 (25lbs at full growth, breed restrictions do apply)<br>
*$25 Pet Rent (max of two pets)<br>
<br>
Nearby Amenities :<br>
*Walking distance to UCR<br>
*Nearby shopping centers<br>
*Local Mall less than 5 miles away<br>
*Near the 215 and 60 Freeway!<br>
<br>
<br>
Contact a helpful office member for more details. You may call or email to get more information on reserving your new home! We will request the last four check stubs (current and consecutive) or three months of bank statements (current and consecutive) for us to income qualify and we will email you the link to apply online.<br>
<br>
The reservation fee ($100) is refundable within the first three days or if you are unresponsive and/or declined for any reason. Once application is approved and you have gone through the entire screening process, the holding deposit will go toward your security deposit. Contact us today to get our detailed screening criteria!<br>
